ibotan\u2019<\/li>\n<li><strong>T\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc kh\u00e1c<\/strong> : Gymnocalycium mihanovichii var. friedrichii f. rubra, Gymnocalycium mihanovichii var. rubrum, Gymnocalycium mihanovichii f. rubra, Gymnocalycium friedrichii \u2018Rubra\u2019<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><strong><u>Ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i khoa h\u1ecdc<\/u><\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Ph\u00e2n h\u1ecd:<\/strong> Cactoideae<\/li>\n<li><strong>B\u1ed9:<\/strong> Trichocereeae<\/li>\n<li><strong>Chi:<\/strong> Gymnocalycium<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a lo\u00e0i <a href=\"https:\/\/cayxinh.vn\/tin-tuc\/xuong-rong\">x\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ed3ng<\/a> n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u d\u1eb9t ho\u1eb7c k\u00e9o d\u00e0i, c\u00f3 m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng, v\u00e0ng, cam, \u0111\u1ecf, t\u00edm ph\u1edbt xanh l\u00e1, n\u00e2u \u0111\u1ecf ho\u1eb7c m\u00e0u nho ch\u00edn, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cao \u0111\u1ebfn cao t\u1edbi 10 cm v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng k\u00ednh l\u00ean t\u1edbi 25 cm, th\u01b0\u1eddng cho nh\u00e1nh con t\u1eeb hai b\u00ean. C\u00e2y c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 8 \u0111\u1ebfn 14 v\u00e2n , r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e2u \u0111\u1eadm quanh th\u00e2n, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf. C\u00e1c gai c\u00f3 m\u00e0u n\u00e2u nh\u1ea1t, h\u01a1i xo\u1eafn, d\u00e0i t\u1edbi 1 cm. Hoa c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang c\u00f3 m\u00e0u h\u1ed3ng nh\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0u t\u00edm, d\u00e0i t\u1edbi 7,5 cm. Qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a lo\u00e0i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u00e0u xanh x\u00e1m ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1edbt h\u1ed3ng, d\u00e0i 4cm v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng k\u00ednh 1cm.<br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5898\" src=\"https:\/\/cayxinh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/Gymnocalycium-mihanovichii.jpg\" alt=\"x\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ed3ng Gymnocalycium\" width=\"721\" height=\"510\" \/><br \/>\n&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><strong><u>C\u00e1ch tr\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u00e2y<\/u><